  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/53b773419e7d944d444f3fe84a41cbd4.avif?t=1758840647\" width=615 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zone 6 is a 1 -4 player narrative exploration game which can be played alone, or with friends.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/b51da0f4449fb14cb2d38fef50c10c75.poster.avif?t=1758840647\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/b51da0f4449fb14cb2d38fef50c10c75.webm?t=1758840647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/b51da0f4449fb14cb2d38fef50c10c75.mp4?t=1758840647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A neon-lit metropolis in the middle of a frosty wasteland, where battered technology, stray magic, and faction rivalries entwine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/2c49a2c226d7e78213627a2b17fc4d50.poster.avif?t=1758840647\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/2c49a2c226d7e78213627a2b17fc4d50.webm?t=1758840647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/2c49a2c226d7e78213627a2b17fc4d50.mp4?t=1758840647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose 1 up to 4 of the indebted adventurers trying to escape their past mistakes which forces them out into the dangerous wasteland in hopes of clearing their debts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/f173f7e93634ad0652e53aaaac9b37ba.poster.avif?t=1758840647\" width=600 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/f173f7e93634ad0652e53aaaac9b37ba.webm?t=1758840647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/f173f7e93634ad0652e53aaaac9b37ba.mp4?t=1758840647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid the creatures lurking about while venturing into the icy frontier haunted by unknown entities, where each discovery carries a grave risk of corrupted power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/b0e1de7a4b18e1e92b16eba3bfbc7177.poster.avif?t=1758840647\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/b0e1de7a4b18e1e92b16eba3bfbc7177.webm?t=1758840647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/b0e1de7a4b18e1e92b16eba3bfbc7177.mp4?t=1758840647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world, where actions might have consequences...? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2813590/extras/371a82cc2115b4f339d43fb1abacd983.avif?t=1758840647\" width=615 height=183 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mediocre artwork by non award-winning Ullbors. (TABS, TABG, Stick Fight and ROUNDS)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soundtrack by Jussi Edefors, created while doing book keeping for clients. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Programming by Tony Backman, while secretly working on a boardgame.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Art by Myra Hild!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sound Effects by Simon Haglund. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
